summary:
Bytescout PDF To HTML SDK converts PDF to HTML without any additional software required.

ByteScout (c) 2008-2017

System Requirements: .NET Framework 2.0 or later
Works with: .NET, ASP.NET, ActiveX, Visual Basic 6, Classic ASP, Delphi and others.

Benefits:

- Converts PDF to HTML with layout preserved;
- Text, fonts, images, tables are preserved;
- Vector graphics is preserved (as a background images);
- Precise positioning of text and images to reproduce the original PDF document design;
- Doesn't require Adobe Reader or any other 3rd-party software to be installed;
- Works with .NET Framework 2.0 and later;
- Provides ActiveX interface to use from legacy programming languages (Visual Basic 6, Delphi) and scripting (VBscript, JScript and others).

Web-site: 
http://bytescout.com/
